# Internal / non-public workspace (kept local, excluded from the public repo).
# BMM planning + implementation artifacts, AI-tooling skill trees, and
# operational status notes. None of this is needed to build, test, or
# reproduce the project — that lives in src/, tests/, configs/,
# pre-registration/, and the public docs (README, REPRODUCE, CHANGELOG).
_bmad/
_bmad-output/
